      <section id="top" class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-inner">
          <div class="hero-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">A better alternative to PowerPoint • open source • self-hosted</p>
            <h1>It’s time for something better than PowerPoint.</h1>
            <p class="lead">
              Deckyard is a web-based presentation system designed for speed and control: build faster with governed
              slide building blocks, present confidently, publish as a link or embed, and add built-in interactivity.
              It’s open source and self-hosted, so you control your data and your platform.
            </p>

            <div class="cta-row">
              <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/docs/product/getting-started/">
                Get started (self-host)
              </a>
              <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" href="/docs/">
                Read the docs
              </a>
            </div>

            <p class="cta-note">Demo note: the local app runs separately (typically on `http://localhost:4177`).</p>

            <ul class="badge-row" aria-label="Highlights">
              <li class="badge">Web-based (no desktop app)</li>
              <li class="badge">Easy publishing + embeds</li>
              <li class="badge">Built-in interactivity</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

